      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new, you\u2019ve found it! This beauty has been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in absolutely flawless shape. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
