    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a true showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like finish protected by a high-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips or swirls. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the dash is free of sun damage, and every single electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a spotless engine bay and a comprehensive service history documented from day one. It drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor\u2014tight, responsive, and silent. This sale includes the original window sticker, two sets of keys, and a custom-fitted car cover. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a time-capsule vehicle.",
      "price": 44900.0,
