      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S in impeccable condition. This 996.2 variant features the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The wide-body Turbo-spec chassis is paired with a factory M030 sport suspension and a viscous-coupling AWD system for superior lateral grip. Mechanically addressed with a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement. The braking system retains its original bite with four-piston monobloc calipers over ventilated, cross-drilled rotors. Zero bore scoring confirmed; paint meter readings are uniform across all panels. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector demanding mechanical perfection.",
